-- Bank of America CEO Lewis to retire by end of the year: report
-- 
-- Wed Sep 30, 2009 5:33pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/09/30/us-bofa-lewis-idUSTRE58T78G20090930

 

 (Reuters) - Bank of America Corp CEO Ken Lewis will retire by end of the year, CNBC reported on Wednesday, citing sources. 

 Other highlights: * CEO ken lewis leaving voluntarily-CNBC, citing sources * Has not decided on successor for Lewis Yet-CNBC, citing sources